## Future Research

1. We need a short price path that contains all of the following:

* For each "drop" and "increase" in price of 10%, 30%, 70%
	* one variation where venues are in sync and just have jitter
		* one variation where price recovers to 20% of the original
		* one variation where price recovers to 50% of the original
		* one variation where price recovers to 90% of the original
	* one variation where venues diverge with 10x the normal jitter
* some period of mild volatility in between with venues in sync within normal jitter
* real price is still MEAN of all venues (un weighted)

This should be a new parameter in the CLI called `----data-source synthetic` that will do this, and it will reject --from and so on.

